description: Fork of Pop COSMIC: Binds Pop Launcher on Super-Key when Pop COSMIC Extension is disabled. Since Pop!_OS moves to its own desktop enviroment (COSMIC DE) and I left linux behind me this extension will not get continued. If you want to change the support manually, modify '~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/pop-launcher-super-key@ManeLippert/metadata.json' under 'shell-version' add the desired version (e.g '44' for GNOME 44).
name: Pop Launcher Super-Key
